Class UniqueHashedMedia

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exedio.cope.Feature
      • com.exedio.cope.Pattern
        • com.exedio.cope.pattern.UniqueHashedMedia
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Copyable, Settable<Media.Value>, Serializable

    public final class UniqueHashedMedia
extends Pattern
implements Settable<Media.Value>, Copyable
    Pattern which wraps a Media and applies a hash string. This allows uniqueness.
    Author:
    knoefel
